PRESS DIGEST - Top Japan business news - Feb 7 . NIHON KEIZAI SHIMBUNDepartment store chain Marui Co Ltd is expected to see around 32 billion yen in pre - tax profits in the business year to January 1998 , up five percent from the same period a year earlier , helped by robust sales of accessories and apparel for young people , as well as the renovation of existing stores . - - - - Canon Sales Co Inc is seen increasing its pre - tax profit by four percent to 22 . 3 billion yen from a year ago in the business year ended December 1996 , thanks to strong sales of personal computers and printers . - - - - 
